/* -> h.MenuD
 *
 * Menu subdivision numbers for Paint
 *
 * Author:  David Elworthy
 * Version: 0.10
 * History: 0.10 -  1 Sept 1989 - created
 *
 * This file just contains symbolic codes for all the menu subdivisions used
 * in the menu trees of Paint.
 */

